items.name: Bacon, Egg and Cheese Breakfast
items.description: Start your day in a sizzlin' way with crispy bacon, egg and melty cheese on fresh toasted Flatbread or whatever you like. It's hard to imagine this trio of tasty ingredients could get even better, but just wait till you try it with everything from juicy tomatoes to spicy jalapenos for a full on flavor free-for-all.

items.name: Black Forest Ham, Egg and Cheese Breakfast
items.description: Helllooo delicious! Enjoy savoury ham, melted cheese, and egg all on a on 3" flatbread.

items.name: B.M.T Melt Breakfast
items.description: Fluffy egg omelet, ham, salami and spicy pepperoni come together with bubbly melted cheese for a morning masterpiece worthy of the breakfast hall of fame. Try it today on a hot toasted flatbread with all your favorite crisp veggies.

items.name: Egg and Cheese Omelet Breakfast
items.description: A classic for a reason. Our egg and cheese is simply delicious. Enjoy a fluffy egg omelet with melted cheese fresh toasted on freshly baked bread. It's unbeatable.

items.name: Steak, Egg and Cheese Breakfast
items.description: No matter what side of the bed you wake up on, you'll love this. Yummy egg with tender and delicious steak. All covered in melty cheese on freshly baked bread. Oh, what a beautiful breakfast.

items.name: Sunrise Subway Melt Breakfast
items.description: Rise and shine to a delightfully delicious breakfast of tender turkey, crispy bacon, ham and fluffy egg under a blanket of bubbly melted cheese. Try one today on hot toasted flatbread with your choice of tasty veggies.

items.name: Bacon, Egg and Cheese Breakfast Meal
items.description: Start your day in a sizzlin' way with crispy bacon, egg and melty cheese on fresh toasted flatbread or whatever you like. items.name: Bacon, Egg and Cheese Sub Breakfast
items.description: Start your day in a sizzlin' way with crispy bacon, egg and melty cheese on fresh toasted flatbread or whatever you like. It's hard to imagine this trio of tasty ingredients could get even better, but just wait till you try it with everything from juicy tomatoes to spicy jalapenos for a full on flavor free-for-all.

items.name: Black Forest Ham, Egg and Cheese Sub Breakfast
items.description: Enjoy savoury ham, melted cheese, and egg all on a on 3" flatbread. Add your choice of toasty veggies for a tasty way to start the day!

items.name: Breakfast B.M.T Melt
items.description: Fluffy egg omelet, ham, salami and spicy pepperoni come together with bubbly melted cheese for a morning masterpiece worthy of the breakfast hall of fame. Try it today on a hot toasted flatbread with all your favorite crisp veggies.

items.name: Egg and Cheese Omelet Sub Breakfast
items.description: A classic for a reason. Our egg and cheese is simply delicious. Enjoy a fluffy egg omelet with melted cheese fresh toasted on freshly baked bread. It's unbeatable.

items.name: Steak, Egg and Cheese Sub Breakfast
items.description: No matter what side of the bed you wake up on, you'll love this. Yummy egg with tender and delicious steak. All covered in melty cheese on freshly baked bread. Oh, what a beautiful breakfast.

items.name: Sunrise Subway Melt Breakfast
items.description: Rise and shine to a delightfully delicious breakfast of tender turkey, crispy bacon, ham and fluffy egg under a blanket of bubbly melted cheese. Try one today on hot toasted flatbread with your choice of tasty veggies.

items.name: Bacon, Egg and Cheese Sub Meal Breakfast
items.description: Start your day in a sizzlin' way with crispy bacon, egg and melty cheese on fresh toasted Flatbread or whatever you like. It's hard to imagine this trio of tasty ingredients could get even better, but just wait till you try it with everything from juicy tomatoes to spicy jalapenos for a full on flavor free-for-all. Served with choice of side and choice of drink.

items.name: Black Forest Ham, Egg and Cheese Sub Meal Breakfast

items.description: No matter what side of the bed you wake up on, you'll love this. Yummy egg with tender and delicious steak. All covered in melty cheese on freshly baked bread. Oh, what a beautiful breakfast. Served with choice of side and choice of drink.

items.name: Autumn Carved Turkey Chopped Salad
items.description: This season, fall for the new autumn carved turkey sandwich. Enjoy all the classic, oven-roasted flavor of thick-cut carved turkey with the sweetness of cranberry mustard sauce. Top it all off with sliced cheddar cheese and crisp veggies on freshly baked bread and you've got fall flavor at its finest.

items.name: B.L.T. Chopped Salad
items.description: The sub that proves great things come in threes. In this case, those three things happen to be crisp bacon, lettuce and juicy tomato. While there's no scientific way of proving it, this B.L.T. might be the most perfect sub in existence.

items.name: Black Forest Ham Chopped Salad
items.description: The Black Forest ham has never been better. Load it up with all the crunchy veggies you like on your choice of freshly baked bread. Even try it fresh toasted with melty cheese and mustard.

items.name: Buffalo Chicken Chopped Salad
items.description: You might wonder how something could taste this incredible. But when you bite into a sandwich this tender, juicy and irresistibly bold, the only thing you need to question is how soon is too soon to have another.

items.name: Carved Turkey Chopped Salad
items.description: It's tender. It's juicy. It’s our New premium, thick-sliced carved turkey served on freshly baked bread. Featuring 100% white meat, no artificial preservatives, and classic oven-roasted flavor. Enjoy as is, or top off your sub with any of our cheeses and fresh veggies.

items.name: Chicken and Bacon Ranch Melt Chopped Salad
items.description: Saddle up and try the fresh toasted Subway chicken and bacon ranch melt sandwich. Stuffed with melted Monterey cheddar cheese, tender all-white meat chicken, crispy bacon, lettuce, tomato, onions and green peppers.

items.name: Cold Cut Combo Chopped Salad
items.description: The cold cut combo is stacked with turkey-based meats - Black Forest ham, Genoa salami and bologna. It's topped with crisp vegetables and served on freshly baked bread. This combo has a little bit of everything.

items.name: Italian B.M.T. Chopped Salad
items.description: This all-time Italian classic is filled with Genoa salami, spicy pepperoni, and Black Forest ham. Get it made the way you say with your favorite veggies on freshly baked bread.

items.name: Italian Hero Chopped Salad
items.description: 1 bite of this hero and you’re bound for Italy. With three flavor-packed Italian deli meats: our new spiced capicola, new cracked-pepper-seasoned Mortadella and our always-delicious spicy Genoa salami Topped with melted provolone, red wine vinegar, and olive oil.

items.name: Meatball Marinara Chopped Salad
items.description: A Subway restaurants favorite. Enjoy Italian style meatballs drenched in irresistible marinara sauce, served on freshly baked bread.

items.name: Oven Roasted Chicken Chopped Salad
items.description: The oven roasted chicken you love is piled high atop freshly baked bread with your favorite toppings from spicy jalapenos to crisp green peppers.

items.name: Pizza Sub Melt Chopped Salad
items.description: Hot outta the oven, it’s the pizza sub with cheese. Enjoy spicy pepperoni, piled high and layered with melt-a-licious cheese and our signature marinara sauce.

items.name: Roast Beef Chopped Salad
items.description: This tasty number, with less than 6 g of fat, is piled high with lean roast beef and your choice of fresh veggies, like crisp green peppers and juicy tomatoes. Try it with some spicy jalapenos for a kick in the taste buds.

items.name: Rotisserie-Style Chicken Chopped Salad
items.description: It's alright to flip out over our new chicken. The new rotisserie-style chicken sandwich is made with tender, hand-pulled all white meat chicken, raised without antibiotics. Try it with crisp veggies on freshly baked bread.

items.name: Spicy Italian Chopped Salad
items.description: A blend of pepperoni and salami, topped with cheese - try it with hot peppers, or your choice of crisp veggies and condiments served hot on freshly baked bread.

items.name: Steak and Cheese Chopped Salad
items.description: The 2 most elemental, irresistible ingredients in the world - piled high onto freshly baked bread and your choice of crisp veggies.

items.name: Subway Club Chopped Salad
items.description: Tender sliced turkey breast, lean roast beef and tasty Black Forest ham come together with your choice of fresh veggies for a low-fat flavor fiesta. Try it today on freshly baked bread and experience all the deliciously for 6 grams of fat.

items.name: Subway Melt Chopped Salad
items.description: Imagine freshly baked bread stuffed with tender sliced turkey, ham, crispy bacon, melted cheese, and your choice of tasty vegetables and condiments. Now, stop imagining and get your mouth over to your nearest Subway restaurant.

items.description: This gourmet specialty features our all white meat teriyaki glazed chicken strips, raised without antibiotics, and our own fat-free sweet onion sauce. With a taste so big, you won't believe it has less than 6 g of fat.

items.name: Tuna Chopped Salad
items.description: Our tasty tuna sandwich is simply sumptuous. Flaked tuna, mixed with mayo, and your choice of vegetables, this local favorite can be built to suit your craving.

items.description: A sandwich so deliciously hearty, you won't know you're eating low-fat. Enjoy the flavor of tender sliced turkey breast and Black Forest ham with your favorite veggies from juicy tomatoes to red onions served on your favorite freshly baked bread.

items.description: Crispy, crunchy and classically delicious. The veggie delite is tangible proof that a sandwich can be high in flavor without being high in fat. Try it today on freshly baked bread and experience all the deliciously for 6 grams of fat. Served with choice of side and choice of drink.

items.name: Sweet Onion Chicken Teriyaki Fresh Fit Sandwich Meal
items.description: This gourmet specialty features our all white meat teriyaki glazed chicken strips, raised without antibiotics, and our own fat-free sweet onion sauce. With a taste so big, you won't believe it has less than 6 g of fat! Served with choice of side and choice of drink.

items.name: Turkey Breast Fresh Fit Sandwich Meal
items.description: Get flavor without the flab when you try this American classic. Dive into tender turkey breast piled sky-high with everything from lettuce and tomatoes to banana peppers, maybe even jalapeños if you're feeling spicy. Served with choice of side and choice of drink.

items.name: Turkey Breast and Black Forest Ham Fresh Fit Sandwich Meal
items.description: A sandwich so deliciously hearty, you won't know you're eating low-fat. Enjoy the flavor of tender sliced turkey breast and Black Forest ham with your favorite veggies from juicy tomatoes to red onions served on your favorite freshly baked bread. Served with choice of side and choice of drink.

items.name: Veggie Delite Fresh Fit Sandwich Meal
items.description: Crispy, crunchy and classically delicious. The veggie delite is tangible proof that a sandwich can be high in flavour without being high in fat. Try a delicious combination of lettuce, tomatoes, green peppers, cucumbers and onions with your choice of fat-free condiments on freshly baked bread. Served with choice of side and choice of drink.

items.name: Kids Black Forest Ham Meal
items.description: Every kid likes to ham it up once in a while. That’s why they’ll love the taste of our Black Forest ham and their favorite veggies on freshly baked bread. Fresh apple slices and an ice-cold bottle of low fat milk make this better-for-you meal a star.

items.name: Kids Roast Beef Meal
items.description: Lean, delicious roast beef and fresh, crisp veggies make this sandwich an ideal choice for kids with healthy appetites. A side of fresh apple slices and a bottle of ice-cold low-fat milk give kids a better-for-you meal they’re sure to love.

items.name: Kids Turkey Breast Meal
items.description: Kids love the taste of tender turkey breast, freshly baked bread and their favorite veggies. Pair it with fresh apple slices and an ice-cold bottle of low-fat milk and you've got a better-for-you meal that's a big hit with parents and kids alike.

items.name: Kids Veggie Delite Meal
items.description: Our veggie delite kids meal piles all their favorites on freshly baked bread. Add fresh apple slices and an ice-cold bottle of low-fat milk for a tasty meal that's also better-for-them.
